---
---

<section class="snes-about w-full min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a2a] py-20 px-4 md:px-8 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1a1a4a 0%, #000 100%);">
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
    
    <!-- 16-Bit Sprite Avatar Placeholder -->
    <div class="sprite-container border-4 border-gray-400 bg-gray-800 p-2 shrink-0 self-center md:self-start object-pixelated bg-blue-900/50">
      <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/142668300?v=4" alt="David" class="w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48 snes-avatar object-cover" />
    </div>

    <!-- The JRPG Dialog Box -->
    <div class="dialog-box relative w-full border-4 md:border-8 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 md:p-10 shadow-[8px_8px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0000c8] to-[#000088]">
      
      <!-- Name Tag -->
      <div class="absolute -top-6 left-4 bg-gray-200 text-black px-4 py-1 border-2 border-white snes-font font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl">
        DAVID
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="snes-font text-white text-xl md:text-3xl leading-relaxed tracking-wide min-h-[150px]">
        <p class="mb-4 text-shadow-snes text-wrap-balance">
          Greetings! Ich bin Full-Stack Entwickler aus Hünfeld. Neben komplexen Architekturen trainiere ich die <span class="text-yellow-300">DBE-Academy Guild</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-300 text-shadow-snes text-wrap-balance">
          Wenn ich nicht gerade code oder Retro-Games spiele, kümmere ich mich um meine Party-Member: Einen Hund und ein Chamäleon!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Arrow Blinking -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-6 text-white snes-font text-3xl animate-bounce">
        ▼
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .snes-font {
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
  }

  /* Hard pixelated borders for image */
  .snes-avatar {
    image-rendering: pixelated;
    image-rendering: crisp-edges;
    filter: contrast(1.2) saturate(1.5);
  }

  .text-shadow-snes {
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #000;
  }

  .animate-bounce {
    animation: bounce 1s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(10px); }
  }
</style>